<ul>
<li>
<b><font size=+3>Main <u>characteristics</u> of interactive systems (refer
to <a href="f1.htm">figure 1</a>)</font></b></li>
</ul>

<ol>
<ol>
<li>
<b><font size=+2><u>Input </u>-- events triggered by users by means of
input devices.</font></b></li>

<li>
<b><font size=+2>Action by users must trigger an <u>output</u> provided
by the system.</font></b></li>

<li>
<b><font size=+2>Input and output are <u>interleaved</u>.</font></b></li>
</ol>
</ol>

